# SoundImageConverter

A C++ application to convert audio (WAV) files into images (PNG) and back, preserving all data losslessly.

## Project Structure
- `include/`: Header files
- `src/`: Source files
- `lib/`: External libraries
- `tests/`: Unit tests
- `resources/`: Sample assets
- `build/`: Build outputs

## Build Instructions
1. Install CMake and a C++ compiler (e.g., Visual Studio 2022).
2. Open the project folder in Visual Studio.
3. Build using `Build > Build All`.

## Requirements
- C++17
- CMake 3.15+